node.text:
Building @tylerbereman’s Red Bull Imagination 2.0 dream was no easy task 💪 and one of the MANY changes: the start and finish line was removed 🤔 but why? (See below)

📲: Watch the full Red Bull Imagination 2021 Course Reveal, LINK IN BIO ‼️ #RedBullImagination

👉 Stay tuned for new episodes dropping September 21 & 22! 

Eliminating the start and finish line (one of the many changes for Red Bull Imagination 2.0) lends a better session-ing atmosphere to allow the riders to push the course even more. Start and finish line sections create a beaten path between Point A and Point B but BUT NOW riders are free to attack the course any way they see fit. This style has been implemented in pool/bowl session skateboarding contests for years and Tyler wanted to bring this to free ride motocross!

MORE COURSE DETAILS (that sound too good to be true):

➡️ Big Dawg Section: this portion of the course contains the Quarter Pipe with a spine feature on the side for riders to use one jump landing from multiple directions, allowing for more creativity in a small space.

➡️Technical Jib Section: this is the snowboard-style jib-like section including a wallride and hip that riders can hit in opposite directions at the same time.

➡️Transfer Zone, aka a KBUB Kevin Windham ode with the supercross inspired Transfer Zone. This SX Transfer Zone delivers skatepark vibes and a clean slate for expression on a cornucopia of line combos.

#motocross #freeride #DIY #course #dirtbike #dream #redbullmotorsports #givesyouwings

After 18 years and 9 FIM World Championships, the LEGEND, @AntonioCairoli, hangs up his boots - we'll be sad to see you go but excited for what the future will hold 🙏
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#RedBull #RedBullMotorsports

Even the “small” features are massive 🤯 at Red Bull Imagination… witness today’s course reveal via Tyler Bereman’s project‼️link in bio.

👉 #RedBullImagination
👉 Sept 14 - 22, 2021
👉 @tylerbereman @ride100percent @fasthouse_ 

#freeride #creative #session #build #redbullmotorsports #givesyouwings
